channel.title: Bludgeoned to live - Devoid of Joy (idk chill for me) now on SC!
channel.description:
This is an automation experiment. I think it’s pretty sweet, kind of loud kind of chill.
Finally put it up on SoundCloud for the picky listeners. The more I listen to this guy the more I’ve come to enjoy it (which is rare)
https://soundcloud.com/devoidofjoy/bludgeoned-to-live
https://youtu.be/MZWHtWxjPXQ
